data.description: Beautiful N. Columbus home is ready for its new owner! Nicely updated while still maintaining fantastic character - this split level home offers versatility no matter your lifestyle! The entry features custom built ins for backpacks, sports gear etc! The main level living room is spacious w/ lots of natural light & new vinyl flooring! The kitchen w/ new tile backsplash overlooks the dining room! Downstairs is a huge bonus room w/ built ins & fireplace perfect for teens or entertaining! Downstairs also features a bedroom w/ back patio access & half bath - great for guests, in-laws! Upstairs the hall bath has chic updates w/ vanity area, new tile, beautiful cabinets! There are 2 additional guest rooms upstairs as well as the master bedroom w/ private bathroom (shower only). The privacy fenced yard is great for enjoying a fire pit, play set or more. Windsor Park offers a scenic park, lake & clubhouse! Truly a must see at a fantastic value - this home is a must see!
